com.cs.pausis.models
Class DB

java.lang.Object
  com.cs.pausis.models.DB

public class DB
extends Object

This class instantiates the main SQLlite database which is used for storing the user data and all the statistical model values. Also this class facilitates the connection to the database for reading and writing.

Since:
August, 2013
Version:
v1.0
Author:
Olalekan Baruwa
